{"tid":937564,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我仲應唔應該同佢做朋友？","createTime":"2018-12-11T15:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T16:25:56.000Z","uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3f283086de7a6936a3018f58891a516e6d2181","tid":937564,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"最近識左個網友，佢話我份人好特別，想同我做個朋友仔。<br />\n<br />\n然後我地就係電話傾計，佢主要係想講佢既<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來大計</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我： 係，有咩大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：我呢，而家就有個大project, 睇下細佬你玩唔玩，希望征服世界，我要成為世界之王。<br />\n我：點征服呀？<br />\n佢：我打算生產一批野，用軍事力量征服。<br />\n我：哦，咁你動機係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：喇，呀叔我就話你知，呀叔我操緊肌，而家係沙田既地下隧道到。<br />\n我： 下，即係你自己掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：係呀，所以我呢邊收得好差，係用緊數據卡。<br />\n我：圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢：唔洗咁緊張，轉頭比，陪我傾陣計先啦。<br />\n我cut 左佢線。<br />\n<br />\n我既願望係成為香港達文西。我係好想學唔同既野，佢自稱自己係it 奇才，我都想跟佢學下野。 但我唔知道應唔應該相信佢，佢而家想招募隊員玩project。<br />\n<br />\n繼續同佢做朋友  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><em><span style=\"color: violet;\">下面係招募link<br />\n</span></em></ins><a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E6ZuVlNcNwvWWL82xFHFNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE6ZuVlNcNwvWWL82xFHFNw&d=1Z1sGj670G5M%2F2O9TxOohDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=78ccc7df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E6ZuVlNcNwvWWL82xFHFNw</a>"},{"pid":"e9651a02bb291085d39c209bb167d2e05874ad33","tid":937564,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0520d9669e9ec957ba0a28e0c1cfec16c3d01ceb","tid":937564,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":